              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Samples below were sealed in a quartz tube.",
                "Pa: Prepared from 231Pa2O5 by chemical purification,",
                "     and mounted on Al (10 mm in diam).",
                "    The number of atoms (2.589+/-0.128)E+17 was",
                "     determined by photopeak counts of 290 keV gamma",
                "     ray (3.25E+4 years).",
                "Np: Prepared from 237NpO2 by chemical purification to",
                "     exclude 239Pu and 238Pu-241Am.",
                "    The number of atoms (1.112+/-0.046)E+18 was",
                "     determined by photopeak of 233Pa, which was",
                "     produced by alpha-decay and in equilibrium with",
                "     237Np."
              ]
            }
